commitResults.messageTitle: Add model class to encapsulate program data
commitResults.messageBody:
Model class will encapsulate the event manager, contact manager and
quiz manager information, providing another layer of abstraction.

The command factory class will be responsible for initializing
the child command classes by reading the CommandType enum.

The control manager class is responsible for parsing userinput,
and then executing the command instance. It also handles all the
execptions thrown during the executing of command.
